{{Campaignbox Black Hawk War}}

[[Image:william durley.jpg#file|thumb|100px|left|Monumnet located near Polo Il]]

A six man detail carrying despatches from Colonel James M. Strode at Galena to General Henry Atkinson at Dixons Ferry was ambushed on the Galena road. Sergent William Durley was killed and buried near the site of the ambush.

